Update content:
1.10 new stages unlock in Hidden Object mode.
2.Added a function for you to send feedback about the tips provided by the item in the main stage. If you do not understand the tip content, tap the ? mark to send feedback.
3.Added Scanner which can find the hidden items at random.

Update content:
1.10 new stages unlock in Hidden Object mode.
2.Added a function for you to send feedback about the tips provided by the item in the main stage. If you do not understand the tip content, tap the ? mark to send feedback.
3.Added Scanner which can find the hidden items at random.
